expression = re.compile(rfc._EXTENTION_AV_REGEX)
bad_examples = ['has a;'] + [chr(x) for x in range(0, 32)] + [chr(127)]
for bad_example in bad_examples:
    self.assertFalse(bool(expression.fullmatch(bad_example)), msg=
        "Bad Extension AV '{m}' matched by regex".format(m=bad_example))
